    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;docs-internal-guid-e0b6321d-7fff-c643-e446-6b3da369df06&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;J&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;osé Rizal began formal schooling at age &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; in Biñan, Laguna, under the strict teacher &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Justiniano Aquino Cruz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;. Here, he excelled academically, honing discipline, perseverance, and intellectual curiosity, which prepared him for future challenges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;In 1877, Rizal transferred to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Ateneo Municipal de Manila&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, enrolling in the Bachelor of Arts program. Driven by a passion for learning and reform, he excelled in academics and extracurriculars, earning numerous honors in literature, oratory, philosophy, fine arts, and science. Graduating magna cum laude, Rizal emerged as one of Ateneo’s top students, showcasing talents in poetry and writing that contributed to Filipino intellectualism.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
